<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Contusion of the hip
joint is a fairly common injury that can be obtained not only in the course of
sports activities, but also in everyday life.&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>It
